==English==
===Noun===
'''breadcrumb'''  (Plural: [[breadcrumbs]])

# a tiny piece of bread, either soft or hard (often used in the [[plural]])
#{{computing}} a description of the [[trail]] of [[page]]s that a user has followed - such as ''Help -> Contents -> Breadcrumb''

===Transitive verb===
'''to breadcrumb'''
#(''cooking'') to [[sprinkle]] breadcrumbs on to a dish, normally before [[cooking]]

